法規內容.條文內容:
In applying for a transcription of the following information to be provided through batch processing by the competent authority, the applicant shall pay a basic transcription fee in a fixed amount of NT$5,000, provided that if the number of the limited partnerships whose information are to be transcribed exceeds 500, an extra transcription fee at the rate of NT$10 per one additional limited partnership shall be charged therefor:
1. Uniform serial number of the limited partnership;
2. Name of the limited partnership;
3. Business to be conducted by the limited partnership;
4. Location of the limited partnership;
5. Name of the limited partnership representative;
6. Name of each general partner; capital contribution amount and liability type of each partner;
7. Actual payment of the installment of capital contribution upon formation; type(s) of non-cash contribution;
8. Duration of the limited partnership;
9. Branch(s) of a domestic limited partnership;
10. Name of the limited partnership responsible person;
11. Name(s) of the limited partnership managerial officer(s);
12. Causes of dissolution agreed by the limited partnership; and
13. Formation registration date of the limited partnership.
